Vinturi Deluxe Wine Aerator with Tower Gift Set
List.Description:
Wine which has been allowed to breathe tastes better. As wine breathes, it opens up, and releases its intended aromas and flavors. This gift set includes the Vinturi Red Wine Aerator and the Vinturi Tower. The Vinturi Red Wine Aerator delivers aeration in the time it takes to pour a glass. Vinturi draws in and mixes the proper amount of air for the right amount of time, allowing your wine to breathe instantly. The results are a better bouquet, enhanced flavor, and a smoother finish. Use the Vinturi Tower to securely hold the Aerator in place while you pour wine through it. Just put your glass under the Aerator and pour! Set also includes a no drip stand, sediment filter, and no-splash gate. Easy to clean and dishwasher safe.




Wine glass and wine not included.
